snippet.title: ekÅ - Malayalam Movie| Official Teaser| Sandeep Pradeep|Dinjith Ayyathan| Mujeeb Majeed|Bahul Ramesh
snippet.description:
Presenting the official teaser of ekÅ, directed by Dinjith Ayyathan, following his acclaimed film Kishkindha Kaandam. Written by Bahul Ramesh, ekÅ marks the final chapter of his Animal Trilogy after Kishkindha Kaandam and Kerala Crime Files: Season 2, forming a collection of three standalone stories sharing a spiritual essence â€” exploring crimes and moral conflicts in a world where animal presence plays a stimulating role. 

The film also marks the maiden production venture of Mr. MRK Jhayaram under his banner Aaradyaa Studios.

Directed by : Dinjith Ayyathan 
Produced by: MRK Jhayaram

Arasan - Official Trailer | Dhanush | Silambarasan TR | Vetri Maaran | Anirudh Ravichander 

This video is made only for showcasing the editing skills of the individual

Arasan is the title of Tamil star Silambarasan TRâ€™s upcoming project with ace filmmaker Vetri Maaran, the makers announced on Tuesday (October 7). Produced by Kalaippuli S Thanu under his V Creations banner, the upcoming film is set in the world of Vetriâ€™s acclaimed 2018 film Vada Chennai.

                    Other details, like the plot, remain unknown. While announcing the film in June, director Vetri Maaran revealed that the film, then tentatively called STR 49, is a parallel narrative set around the same time as Vada Chennai, and that â€œcharacters and aspects from Vada Chennai will find their way into this story.
      
               A previously released promo video of the film showed a sickle-wielding Simbu, in a striped shirt and baggy pants, walking into a desolate lane. The video, however, cuts before his face is revealed. Interestingly, the title poster also intentionally hides the actorâ€™s face, which certainly adds to the mystery.

While cast details have yet to be officially revealed, a leaked still from the set showed director Nelson alongside Simbu, prompting netizens to speculate that the director is playing a cameo in the film. Further speculations added that actors Kavin and Manikandan are also part of the film, and that actors Andrea Jeremiah, Samuthirakani and Kishore are reprising their roles from Vada Chennai. Vada Chennai, widely considered as one of the best gangster dramas in Tamil, featured Dhanush as a young man who is pulled into a world of crime, one where you either do or die. Over the years, the film has attained cult status among audiences. Interestingly, Vetri had also announced a spin-off series centred around Ameer Sultanâ€™s character Rajan, titled Rajan Vagaiyara; however, there havenâ€™t been any updates on the same.

These are derivative works and as such, may find protection from copyright claims under the doctrine of fair use. The trailer mashups are not only a user-generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan-made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot or genre of the film entirely.

snippet.title: Aaromaley - Trailer | Silambarasan TR | Kishen Das | Harshath Khan | Shivathmika | Sarang Thiagu
snippet.description:
A story of love and friendship with a whole lot of fun and drama. Presenting the trailer of Aaromaley. Releasing worldwide from November 7.

With the voice of Silambarasan TR.

Cast: Kishen Das, Harshath Khan, Shivathmika Rajashekar, Megha Akash, VTV Ganesh, Tulasi, Sibi Chakravarthy, Namritha MV, Sandhya Winfred, and others.

snippet.description:

Worldwide Releasing On Oct 31st 2025.

CAST

Prabhas as Sivudu & Baahubali, Rana Daggubati as Bhallaladeva, Anushka Shetty as Devasena, Tamannaah as Avanthika with Ramya Krishna, Nasser, Sathyaraj, Kiccha Sudeepa, Adivi Sesh, Rakesh Varre, Meka Ramakrishna.

CREW

Story: V. Vijayendra Prasad

snippet.title: The Clashteroid - A Hammer Jam Film
snippet.description:
Builder got his hands on a mysterious Meteorite Hammer sent by  @hankschannel ! For the entire Hammer Jam event, Home Village upgrade costs and timers are cut in half, and Resource Collectors produce 2x faster with double capacity. Brace for impact, Chief!

Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter â–º https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram â–º https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook â–º https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok â–º https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-Â­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

snippet.title: Ek Deewane Ki Deewaniyat Mera Hua x Kabhi Jo Badal Barse Mashup | Aftermorning  | Saiyaara | Shreya
snippet.description:
A heartfelt blend of timeless romance and modern soundscapes â€” Ek Deewane Ki Deewaniyat Mera Hua brings together two beautiful worlds through emotion, melody, and passion.
 
More Aftermorning Viral Mashups : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLNSv8z24EefMuPV1lMnw28k5qN341cccz
Subscribe http://bit.ly/aftermorningmusic
Instagram https://www.instagram.com/aftermorningproductions/

Ek Deewane Ki Deewaniyat Mera Hua Mashup | Aftermorning | Harshvardhan | Shreya Ghoshal 
Remix  by : Aftermorning 
Mix Master: Vishal Rajput
Video Edit: Somnath Roy ( Afterlife Visual)
Release : AIDC
Music Production & Other work enquiries: yesugadeabhishek@gmail.com


Mera Hua
Shaam dhalti hai, aur main sochta hoon,
Tere bina bhi, main tujhmein kho jaata hoon.
Kuch lamhe the â€” adhure, kuch sapne the â€” pure,
Par har dafa tu tha, mere dil ke aas-paas zarur.
Yaad hai wo pal, jab tu muskurayi thi,
Waqt ruk gaya tha, khud zindagi sharmaayi thi.
Mujhe laga bas, ab kuch aur na chahiye,
Us ek pal ne, mujhe poora kar diya tha.
Tu door hai, par har subah tere saath uthta hoon,
Khidki se aane waali roshni mein tujhe dhoondhta hoon.
Tere bina bhi, tu mere saath hai,
Har saans mein tera ehsaas hai.
Kabhi socha nahi tha, pyaar itna chupke se aayega,
Zakhmon ko choo kar, dawa ban jaayega.
Tere jaane ke baad bhi, tu yahaan reh gaya,
Khali kamron mein, tera nasha mehka gaya.
Main likhta hoon, toh lafz tera roop le lete hain,
Gungunata hoon, toh sur tera naam keh dete hain.
Har silsilay ka anjaam tu ban gaya,
Main sirf tera thaâ€¦ aur tu mera hua.
Kahin duaon mein, kahin armaanon mein,
Tu likha gaya hai meri kahani ke har gumaanon mein.
Aur chahe duniya keh de ye pyaar bewajah,
Mujhe toh bas itna kehna hai â€”
Tu mera sapna nahiâ€¦ mera sach hua.
Tu mera hua.
